      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1331 - Muhammad ibn Muslim asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about traveling by sea when it is turbulent.\nHe (as) replied: \"Why would a person endanger his life and his religion?\"."
